data.description: Nestled on 5.31 acres of serene lakefront property, this charming farmhouse exudes warmth and elegance. Upon entering, the primary suite welcomes you on the right, while to the left, a doorway leads to the cozy living room with a wood fireplace. Transitioning through, you find the dining area adjacent to the living room, seamlessly connected for entertaining. The open kitchen with a breakfast bar offers convenience. Beyond lies the sunroom, a tranquil retreat. Upstairs, two bedrooms, one with a fireplace, and the other, an oversized bonus room offer comfort. Enjoy year round comfort with the newly installed heating and air conditioning systems. Outside, expansive grounds provide ample space for outdoor activities, with a private dock by the lake.
